# 1. Executive Summary

The ELECTRON-2 Content Generator is the core content production engine
for the CorpFit QUANTUM AI Content Factory. It is a 15-node n8n workflow
that takes a production brief (topic, platform, module, funnel,
duration), generates brand-compliant wellness content using Claude
Sonnet 4, validates it through 3 AI-powered QA gates using Claude Haiku,
and stores the result in PostgreSQL.

The pipeline covers all 5 CorpFit content modules (Steps, Workouts,
Meals, Check-in, Events), both funnels (B2C individual and B2B
corporate), and 4 platforms (TikTok, Instagram, LinkedIn, YouTube). It
produces complete video content briefs including hooks, scripts,
on-screen text, storyboards, captions, CTAs, and disclaimers.

