# 8. Docker Infrastructure

All services run as Docker containers on the Windows laptop 24/7:

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Service**       **Port**    **Container       **Purpose**
                                Name**            
  ----------------- ----------- ----------------- -----------------------
  n8n               :5678       n8n               Workflow automation

  Qdrant            :6333       qdrant            Vector database

  PostgreSQL        :5432       postgres          Persistent storage

  Ollama            :11434      ollama            Local embeddings

  Open WebUI        :3000       open-webui        Chat interface

  Portainer         :9000       portainer         Docker management
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

> ⚠️ *CRITICAL: In n8n Code nodes, always use Docker container names
> (qdrant, ollama, postgres) NOT localhost. Services communicate via
> Docker network.*

